export class ArchitectureGovernanceService {
  public async validateContinuously(): Promise<void> {
    const violations = await this.analyzeCodebase();
    const suggestions = await this.generateImprovements(violations);

    if (violations.length > 0) {
      await this.createImprovementTasks(suggestions);
    }
  }
}
```

**Advanced Metrics**:
- Real-time architecture compliance monitoring
- Automated refactoring suggestions
- Architecture evolution tracking
- Performance impact analysis

### 1.2 AI-First Architecture

#### Basic Implementation (Week 2-3)
**Prerequisites**: Basic understanding of APIs and AI concepts
**Timeline**: 2-3 weeks  
**Resources**: 2-3 developers, basic AI/ML knowledge

**Step 1: API Accessibility Assessment**
